I have interviewed dozens of web designers/programmers through Upwork. And I've worked with several over the past 10-15 years. Vinayak and his work are the best of the best. He provided a competitive bid and successfully provided all of the services he promised. He was collaborative, communicative, and open to my ideas, notes, and revisions. When something didn't look or function the way I envisioned, Vinayak quickly worked to correct it. He went above and beyond, and I now have a website that is aesthetically pleasing and functions perfectly. I'll definitely be working with him on future projects and highly recommend his services.

Justin Colon
